# SmartSpend AI

## Overview

SmartSpend AI is an AI-powered personal finance and expense management platform designed to help users track spending, analyze financial habits, create budgets, and receive intelligent recommendations for improving financial health.

## Problem Statement

Many individuals struggle to understand where their money goes each month. Traditional budgeting tools often require significant manual effort and provide limited insights. SmartSpend AI addresses this challenge by automatically categorizing expenses, identifying spending patterns, and delivering actionable recommendations.

## Key Features

* AI-powered expense categorization
* Real-time spending analytics
* Budget planning and tracking
* Personalized savings recommendations
* Financial goal management
* Spending trend visualization
* Monthly financial reports
* Smart alerts for unusual transactions
* Multi-account support
* Secure data storage and privacy protection

## Target Users

* Individuals managing personal finances
* Students tracking expenses
* Families creating household budgets
* Freelancers and independent professionals
* Small business owners monitoring expenses

